{
  "texts": [
    "Even with nouns there are issues with polysemy, i.e., words with multiple meanings and thus multiple different common contexts.",
    "To help with this problem, we use Gensimfoot_10 using NPMI to extract meaningful n-grams [10].",
    "An n-gram is a combination of n adjacent tokens into a single token so that a term such as \"microsoft_windows\" can be found and the computer operating system can be distinguished from the windows of a building.",
    "We apply two iterations so that longer n-grams such as \"law_enforcement_ agencies\" can be found.",
    "To support different languages, we use connector words specific to each language."
  ]
}